Biclique<V extends java.lang.Comparable<? super V>,E extends java.lang.Comparable<? super E>> - Class in bicliques.graphs
Class implements a complete bipartite graph (biclique) with methods for computing maximal bicliques.
Biclique(Graph<V, E>, Set<Graph.Vertex<V>>, Set<Graph.Vertex<V>>) - Constructor for class bicliques.graphs.Biclique
Constructs a biclique on two disjoint sets of vertices.

Constructs a maximal biclique on a generating set of vertices.
Biclique(Graph<V, E>, Graph.Vertex<V>) - Constructor for class bicliques.graphs.Biclique
Constructs a maximal biclique on a generating set of vertices containing only one vertex (maximal biclique generated from a star biclique).

Constructs a biclique containing just the two vertices.
